927
00:56:20,690 --> 00:56:23,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika pergi, aku enggan bicara dengan Kakak lagi.</font>

928
00:56:23,590 --> 00:56:25,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Bibi juga harus berkemas dan pergi.</font>

929
00:56:25,959 --> 00:56:27,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Memangnya Bibi bisa tinggal di rumah ini?</font>

930
00:56:27,900 --> 00:56:30,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Diam. Akan kusobek mulutmu itu.</font>

931
00:56:30,969 --> 00:56:33,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Pil Soon, kemasi barangmu.</font>

932
00:56:34,539 --> 00:56:35,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu tidak boleh tinggal di sini.</font>

933
00:56:35,969 --> 00:56:38,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak, yang benar saja.</font>

934
00:56:38,370 --> 00:56:40,539
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak akan lari seperti pengecut?</font>

935
00:56:40,610 --> 00:56:41,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

936
00:56:44,350 --> 00:56:45,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang Ayah lakukan?</font>

937
00:56:46,319 --> 00:56:48,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah pikir rumah ini hanya milik Ayah?</font>

938
00:56:48,779 --> 00:56:50,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku lahir di sini,</font>

939
00:56:50,150 --> 00:56:53,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu dan Nenek juga tinggal di sini. Bisa-bisanya...</font>

940
00:56:53,590 --> 00:56:56,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa-bisanya Ayah membiarkan para jalang itu merampas rumah kita?</font>

941
00:56:56,789 --> 00:56:59,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak bisa. Batalkan semuanya.</font>

942
00:56:59,400 --> 00:57:02,799
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak bisa dibatalkan. Kontraknya sudah ditandatangani.</font>

943
00:57:03,430 --> 00:57:04,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir.</font>

944
00:57:04,900 --> 00:57:08,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah sudah melepaskan rumah ini.</font>

945
00:57:08,140 --> 00:57:10,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, pergi saja sendiri.</font>

946
00:57:11,739 --> 00:57:13,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami akan melindungi rumah ini.</font>

947
00:57:14,680 --> 00:57:17,080
<font color=#FFFF00>- Apa?/- Se Joon, aku,</font>

948
00:57:17,080 --> 00:57:18,410
<font color=#FFFF00>dan Ki Chan...</font>

949
00:57:19,279 --> 00:57:22,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan, Se Hu</font>

950
00:57:23,090 --> 00:57:24,620
<font color=#FFFF00>akan melindunginya.</font>

951
00:57:26,920 --> 00:57:29,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Se Hu?</font>

952
00:57:29,630 --> 00:57:31,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa Se Hu?</font>

953
00:57:32,130 --> 00:57:35,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan kamu, benar?</font>

954
00:57:35,600 --> 00:57:38,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang terjadi?</font>

955
00:57:38,469 --> 00:57:41,299
<font color=#FFFF00>Bu Lee, Anda benar-benar tidak punya hati nurani.</font>

956
00:57:41,440 --> 00:57:43,309
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda tidak takut tinggal di sini?</font>

957
00:57:43,309 --> 00:57:44,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda membunuh Nenek di sini.</font>

958
00:57:45,370 --> 00:57:47,509
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena Anda, Nenek meninggal.</font>

959
00:57:47,739 --> 00:57:49,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Se Joon, kamu...</font>

960
00:57:49,850 --> 00:57:52,509
<font color=#FFFF00>Se Joon, kenapa berkata begitu kepada ibumu?</font>

961
00:57:52,509 --> 00:57:56,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Dal Hee, kamu memihaknya karena kamu membantunya?</font>

962
00:57:56,420 --> 00:57:59,090
<font color=#FFFF00>- Apa?/- Ketika Nenek meninggal,</font>

963
00:57:59,319 --> 00:58:01,019
<font color=#FFFF00>kamu juga berada di sana.</font>

964
00:58:01,759 --> 00:58:03,259
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian bersekongkol!</font>

965
00:58:05,059 --> 00:58:06,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya ampun.</font>

966
00:58:07,360 --> 00:58:09,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu?</font>

967
00:58:09,160 --> 00:58:12,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, Dal Hee juga berada di lokasi kejadian.</font>

968
00:58:12,269 --> 00:58:13,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Nenek jatuh dari tangga.</font>

969
00:58:13,969 --> 00:58:16,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Alih-alih membawanya ke rumah sakit, dia meninggalkannya.</font>

970
00:58:16,140 --> 00:58:18,039
<font color=#FFFF00>Dialah pelakunya, Ayah.</font>

971
00:58:18,039 --> 00:58:19,739
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan.</font>

972
00:58:20,039 --> 00:58:21,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapan kamu akan berhenti membicarakan orang</font>

973
00:58:21,940 --> 00:58:23,610
<font color=#FFFF00>yang telah tiada?</font>

974
00:58:23,880 --> 00:58:25,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bosan mendengarnya.</font>

975
00:58:27,650 --> 00:58:28,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang meninggal?</font>

976
00:58:30,120 --> 00:58:32,549
<font color=#FFFF00>- Apa?/- Jangan berpura-pura.</font>

977
00:58:33,219 --> 00:58:34,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Nenek masih hidup!</font>

978
00:58:40,559 --> 00:58:41,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya ampun.</font>

979
00:58:42,059 --> 00:58:45,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksud kalian?</font>

980
00:58:45,900 --> 00:58:47,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibuku...</font>

981
00:58:47,370 --> 00:58:50,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibuku masih hidup? Benarkah?</font>

982
00:58:50,110 --> 00:58:51,569
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan menipu kami.</font>

983
00:58:52,009 --> 00:58:54,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Beraninya kamu tidak hormat terhadap orang meninggal?</font>

984
00:58:55,009 --> 00:58:56,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia masih hidup.</font>

985
00:59:00,249 --> 00:59:01,549
<font color=#FFFF00>Se Hu,</font>

986
00:59:02,920 --> 00:59:04,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Sayang.</font>

987
00:59:06,660 --> 00:59:07,719
<font color=#FFFF00>Se Hu.</font>

988
00:59:09,690 --> 00:59:11,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibuku masih hidup.</font>

989
00:59:11,630 --> 00:59:13,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yakin ini suaranya.</font>

990
00:59:16,069 --> 00:59:19,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh? Dia masih hidup?</font>

991
00:59:20,900 --> 00:59:22,239
<font color=#FFFF00>Di mana dia?</font>

992
00:59:22,870 --> 00:59:25,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Di mana dia sekarang?</font>

993
00:59:25,969 --> 00:59:27,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia akan datang sebentar lagi.</font>

994
00:59:28,209 --> 00:59:29,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

995
00:59:44,590 --> 00:59:46,029
<font color=#FFFF00>"Terima kasih untuk Park Jun Keum dan Lee Yu Ri"</font>

996
01:00:02,950 --> 01:00:05,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Masuklah. Kenapa lama sekali?</font>

997
01:00:05,749 --> 01:00:07,019
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ini, ya?/- Bacalah.</font>

998
01:00:07,420 --> 01:00:08,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sangat penasaran.</font>

999
01:00:08,580 --> 01:00:09,719
<font color=#FFFF00>"Dia tidak merobeknya?"</font>

1000
01:00:10,920 --> 01:00:12,219
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa tidak kamu lihat?</font>

1001
01:00:13,160 --> 01:00:14,660
<font color=#FFFF00>- Berlatih?/- Kita sedang berlatih.</font>

1002
01:00:14,660 --> 01:00:16,090
<font color=#FFFF00>- Tidak./- Ya ampun.</font>

1003
01:00:16,090 --> 01:00:17,430
<font color=#FFFF00>"Kita sedang syuting"</font>

1004
01:00:17,630 --> 01:00:19,330
<font color=#FFFF00>- Berdiri./- Jangan, Pimpinan.</font>

1005
01:00:19,759 --> 01:00:21,430
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dia tidak bisa pergi sekarang./- Minggir!</font>

1006
01:00:21,430 --> 01:00:22,499
<font color=#FFFF00>"Melempar"</font>

1007
01:00:22,499 --> 01:00:24,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Pimpinan.</font>

1008
01:00:25,799 --> 01:00:27,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu baik-baik saja?</font>

1009
01:00:29,039 --> 01:00:30,739
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu hampir melemparnya.</font>

1010
01:00:30,739 --> 01:00:31,969
<font color=#FFFF00>"Tidak kusangka ini adegan aksi"</font>

